The paper discusses the development of artificial intelligent services, which falls under the category of cs.AI. The proposed method involves matrix factorization, which is commonly used in machine learning and falls under the category of cs.LG. The paper also discusses the extraction of rule-like model explanations, which falls under the category of cs.CL. The experiment results involve the use of open datasets as well as an industry dataset, which falls under the category of cs.CE. Finally, the paper discusses the importance of inspecting the underlying decision making logic, which falls under the category of cs.CR.
